OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FGenerally
OL,6,Fdry with some clear spells at first
OL,7,Fthis evening, but cloud thickening
OL,8,Ffrom the west towards midnight,
OL,9,Fbringing some patchy rain and drizzle
OL,10,Feastwards through the early hours.
OL,11,FWinds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA rather cloudy start, with
OL,14,Fsome patchy light rain or drizzle.
OL,15,FHowever, becoming mostly dry into the
OL,16,Fafternoon with bright intervals
OL,17,Fdeveloping. Feeling noticeably milder
OL,18,Fwith just a gentle breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
