OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday rather cloudy, damp across
OL,7,Fwestern hills, elsewhere drier. Mild.
OL,8,FRain band moving south overnight,
OL,9,FThursday, probably brighter and
OL,10,Fcooler. Friday, variable cloud, patchy
OL,11,Frain easing. Wet and windy later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
